{"tid":428482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，今次之後反而對曹星如改觀","createTime":"2017-10-08T06:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T12:24:01.000Z","uid":37522,"like":62,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce3adb6f184924419ed2705789814052c518b46","tid":428482,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"我之前一直都覺得佢揀廢對手，刷數據。今次睇都係想睇河野公平打柒佢。<br />\n<br />\n今場佢贏係好似有d勝之不武，但係反而睇得出佢有用腦，捱得同埋有體育精神。見到佢隻眼，望落去都覺得痛，對面仲要下下打落去真係痛到仆街 (咁大個target,俾著我係河野仲唔老死都打隻眼打到你投降) 佢係劣勢度唯一可能可以做既就真係搶分同埋死忍唔投降。佢本來可能都只係想忍到河野冇氣，點知醫生終止左場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次佢贏，係好彩，但係真係靠自己死忍，唔放棄先有機會俾佢贏番黎。"},{"pid":"7689484559ea5403123fdfde6bc8a7a26988fc6b","tid":428482,"uid":80088,"like":6,"dislike":27,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"其實係咪特燈合埋眼，扮開唔番？"},{"pid":"ebb5eaa542739322a9d8d724b641bdfd906f6c47","tid":428482,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":18,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66b62694cec562ba8b204815f1aec0f8be378360","tid":428482,"uid":10795,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"agger估唔到連登仲有人同我差唔多諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為而家個個都一係盲撐一係盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ad354bb6f9e5e6b3a07a9855335061eb6dfc7b","tid":428482,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4d76499d9cbd43945318f00d96773b2f6a613f6","tid":428482,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger估唔到連登仲有人同我差唔多諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為而家個個都一係盲撐一係盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}